        2: int birds = 10;
        3: public static void main(String[] data) {
        4: int trees = 5;
        5: System.out.print(trees+birds);
        6: }
        7: }
        A. It does not compile.
        B. It compiles but throws an exception at runtime.
        C. It compiles and outputs 5.
        D. It compiles and outputs 15.

